data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Discover the epitome of Florida living in this captivating two-story home nestled in the sought-after Rivercrest community. The open layout of the first floor seamlessly blends living spaces, a practical home office, and a convenient half bath. Open Living Room and Sunny dining room are ready to make memories for years to come.  Kitchen with plenty of space to cook with room for bar stool seating too.  Venture upstairs to find a collection of inviting bedrooms, including a spacious primary suite featuring a private bath with a garden tub, two sinks, and a shower. The allure extends outdoors with an extended screened lanai, perfect for year-round enjoyment to grill, dine or lounge on the Lanai.  The lanai is complemented by a fully fenced backyard for added privacy. Recent upgrades, including a newer roof and HVAC system installed just two years ago, ensure peace of mind and longevity. Positioned for convenience near US301, I75, and the Crosstown Expressway for all your commutes.  This home offers easy access to shopping, dining, schools, YMCA, hospitals, and more in this thriving area. Enjoy the community perks, from two pools with a splash zone to playgrounds, tennis courts, and basketball courts. Embrace the Florida lifestyle and make this delightful residence your forever home.
